Guardia toggled her radio and leaned slightly.  &quot;It appears we&#39;ve run into
something.  We&#39;re going to investigate.  Could we get a scanner sweep from
above?&quot;

&quot;Beep....... Passive scanners are not picking up anything,&quot; replied someone
from the shuttle, then Lord Perseus spoke.  &quot;If this is a threat, we can&#39;t
risk lighting up our active scanners.  Given our situation, we need to
maintain a low profile.  Investigate with caution.  If you make contact with
hostiles, try to take cover and we&#39;ll move in to back you up.&quot;

&quot;Rodger...&quot;

Guardia motioned in the direction Tuscon appeared to be pointing, and the
team began to move.

